armagetronad: Armagetron Advanced (a Tron Clone in 3d)
armagetronad:
armagetronad: Armagetron is a multiplayer game in 3d that attempts to
armagetronad: emulate and expand on the lightcycle sequence from the movie
armagetronad: Tron.  It's an old school arcade game slung into the 21st
armagetronad: century.  Highlights include a customizable playing arena,
armagetronad: HUD, unique graphics, and AI bots.  For the more advanced
armagetronad: player there are new game modes and a wide variety of physics
armagetronad: settings to tweak as well. 
armagetronad:
armagetronad: Packaged by Georgi D. Sotirov <gdsotirov@dir.bg>
